data.description: Don't miss this 2016 Fischer built home! 4 Bedroom 2.5 Bath; 2-story; attractive RED BRICK front home. The bright & airy eat-in kitchen features 42" cabinets. At your feet you will find beautiful laminate flooring. This home boasts 9ft ceilings with modern recessed lighting throughout. Upstairs hosts a cozy loft. Enjoy the master suite with double sinks and garden tub with a separate shower. Garage has a 4ft bump out to give extra room. Wander outback to find this home sits on nearly a 1/4-acre lot with a complete privacy fence. Nice patio and a storage shed too! Great neighborhood with walking trails, community pool, etc and plenty of amenities nearby! Book your showing TODAY! It won't last long!
